<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.2.4">
<l>āṉā yarkūṭi yamaitta viḻavai yamarartaṅ</l>
<l>kōṉārk koḻiyak kōvartta ṉattuccey tāṉmalai</l>
<l>vāṉāṭ ṭilniṉṟu māmalark kaṟpakat tottiḻi</l>
<l>tēṉā ṟupāyun teṉtiru māliruñ cōlaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The mountain of he who lifted Govardhana</l>
<l rend="indent">to stop the festival for the king of immortals</l>
<l rend="indent">that was celebrated by the assembled cow herders,</l>
<l>is Tirumāliruñcōlai in the South where a river of honey flows,</l>
<l rend="indent">falling from the huge flower clusters of the Kaṟpaka [tree]</l>
<l rend="indent">standing in the heavenly country.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
